I won! I won against Leif!
Look, he's so mad I managed
to beat him! Haha!

rows.label: qst000703_msg0002

Maybe it was just a stroke of luck
that I met you Drivers, but...

rows.label: qst000703_msg0003
rows.name:
Well, I managed to do what
my mam said, so at the end
of the day, I'm happy!

rows.label: qst000703_msg0004
rows.name: Oh, yeah. Here, with my thanks.

rows.label: qst000703_msg0005

Actually, my mam wanted you
to have this, too.
